Heat grill. Cook rice according to package directions. In small bowl, combine soy sauce, oyster sauce and garlic. Set aside. When grill is heated, place oiled grill basket on grill over medium heat, add steak, mushrooms, onions and corn. Cook and stir frequently for 10 to 15 minutes, or until meat is of desired doneness. During last 5 minutes of cooking, add 1 tablespoon at a time of sauce while stirring. Serve stir-fry over cooked rice.